-- min-max-range.cell: compute min, max, and range of a list
-- Tests: list primitives, multi-cell dependency chain

ÔŐó find-min
  given values Ôëí [3, 1, 4, 1, 5, 9, 2, 6]
  yield minimum

  ÔŐó= minimum ÔćÉ min(values)

  ÔŐĘ minimum = 1

ÔŐó find-max
  given values Ôëí [3, 1, 4, 1, 5, 9, 2, 6]
  yield maximum

  ÔŐó= maximum ÔćÉ max(values)

  ÔŐĘ maximum = 9

ÔŐó compute-range
  given find-minÔćĺminimum
  given find-maxÔćĺmaximum
  yield range

  ÔŐó= range ÔćÉ find-maxÔćĺmaximum - find-minÔćĺminimum

  ÔŐĘ range = 8
